casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Back, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Back, 105 Ohio St.3d 129, 2005-Ohio-782.]

*130(No. 2003-2182 Submitted February 16, 2005 Decided March 16, 2005.) David H. Bodiker, State Public Defender, and Stephen P. Hardwick, Assistant Public Defender, for appellant.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of State v. White, 103 Ohio St.3d 580, 2004-Ohio-5989, 817 N.E.2d 393.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
